Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此有一个区域 所处的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and so there's a domain in between...{\r}
