Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙间存在着叫做水的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the universe has something called water.{\r}
