Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它甚至还随着时间而改变{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And it even changes with time.{\r}
